                        <interp inst="t18360404-name-244" type="given" value="FRANCIS"></interp>FRANCIS SOMES</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Brick-lane and am a pawnbroker. I took in these four razors of the prisoner on the 10th of March, in the name of John Williams—this is the duplicate which my young man gave him.</p>
